## Upper Arm Bushing Removal Note  


Press the upper arm bushing out by using the SSTs and a socket as shown.  

![](images/1.jpg)
  


## Upper Arm Bushing Installation Note  


1. Apply soapy water to the upper arm bushing. 
2. Press the bushing in by using the SST and a socket in the direction of the arrow.  

